casebody.data:
Charles ROGERS, petitioner,
v.
WISCONSIN. No. 13-5549. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013.

Case below, 345 Wis.2d 398, 824 N.W.2d 928.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Wisconsin, District I, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
